org.opends.server.snmp

Class SNMPMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.snmp.SNMPMonitor

  • public class SNMPMonitor
extends Object
    The SNMPMonitor Class allows to get a singleton SNMPMonitor object allowing to access the JMX cn=monitor MBean.
